Name  Type  Use  Default  Fixed  Annotation
ID  xs:ID        
auc:Status  derived by: xs:string        
documentation
Defines whether a system is currently present in the building, or if it is a proposed alternative or past system.

element HVACSystemType/Plants/HeatingPlantType
diagram
namespace http://nrel.gov/schemas/bedes-auc/2014
properties
minOcc 0
maxOcc unbounded
content complex
children auc:Boiler auc:DistrictHeating auc:SolarThermal auc:OtherCombination auc:NoHeating auc:Unknown
attributes
Name  Type  Use  Default  Fixed  Annotation
ID  xs:ID        
auc:Status  derived by: xs:string        
documentation
Defines whether a system is currently present in the building, or if it is a proposed alternative or past system.
annotation
documentation
Type of central heating system, defined as any source of heating energy separate from the zone being heated. Local heating systems (such as packaged systems and fan-coils) are recorded in a separate data field.
